reviewText: I don't know if I ordered this for me or the kids since I've watched it with them and I like it. I think this is great for having kids appreciate the difference in others.

If your looking for the newer version of the doodlebops this isn't it.  The packaging is deceiving, the package has the newer doodlebops where all 3 videos are the first episodes with the bad costumes and bad make-up.  Mattered to me because the deceptive packaging, but my 3 year old doesn't care, she loves them anyway.
Major hit with my 2 year old great nephew!! He wanted to stop his Birthday party to watch the DVD's. Since the party he will not allow his parents to put on a differant DVD.
good movies
Loved it.
Great price for the amount of episodes you get. My grandson loves Bob and the whole gang! You won't be disappointed when you purchase this. Enjoy!!
My son, just over 2 years loves "Bobbob" as he calls him, and we were looking for some basic shows to have on hand for viewing.  This fits the bill with many choices for a great price.

We bought this for my granddaughter. She loves it and watches it often Refreshingly, it contains very little in the way of what I would call "indoctrination" ( a real problem with Sesame street and most of the stuff coming out of NPR, much of which is highly skewed to instill various notions in kids). Recommended.
This DVD pack was a great value for the money. They are very fun to watch and the stories are great!
Nearly two year old grandson loves them.  They were mailed to kyrgyzstan where the lives.  I will now order some Thomas DVDs.

I love Bob the Builder so much that I bought three collections for my great nephew. One for birthday, two for Christmas, and he's going to be beyond thrilled with more Bob. He is three and chants the words to anyone who'll listen, expecting us to finish the chant with him. Seeing him share his excitement with us is worth every penny. Can we build it? YES WE CAN!
I'm very impressed with this item. It's a Christmas gift for my son. The product was packaged beautifully and undamaged.
it meet my approver .my great grand daughter just love it.it will be of services to her for afew more years.
Got this for my Grand Daughter in Japan, she sees this on TV, so she requested for a Birth day Gift.
it was better then the first movie we got wish it was the new ones would be better to watch

These three videos are just the thing form my grandchildren when it is raining out or too cold.

The quality is excellent and the grandchildren really enjoy watching them.
My nephew, two years old, has shown his propensity to enjoy using child sized hand tools. So what could be a more appropriate gift for him than Bob? He watches for hours upon hours.
I buy for my son, like him, came fast, excellent condition, I recommend it. See the face of my son when he saw him is priceless
My 2 year old loves these three dvd's!  We watch them every day and I plan to find more Bob the Builder DVD's soon!
The Doodlebops: Family Fun Pack is an excellent and very entertaining set of educational videos. My son will sit for hours watching them over and over.

My girls randomly saw the Doodlebops one Saturday morning and immediately fell in love, I searched high and low for dvds and was so excited when I finally found some!  They arrived super fast and in great condition!

My grandson enjoys watching this DVD. He has watched it several times. Continue to offer this and other similar items for
purchase.
Barney Family Fun Pack My grand-daughter loves these. She dances and sings swaying to the music. It is calming to a one-year little princess!

Our children really enjoy these movies. I don't hesitate to leave the room as I would with unknown commercials coming on between episodes. They always have a great message; it's not just entertainment.
DVD received on time and as described.  It was a video for my 18mth old Gransdon and he dances to the music.  I'm sure he will appreciate it more when he is older.

My grand daughter is almost 5 months, she loves to watch tv, so i feel if shes going to watch tv then i need to buy dvds so she can learn from them. I was really pleased with this 3 pk dvd set, she likes to hear music with them, giggle bellies is her all time favorite and would you believe they only have 2 dvds out. I was told by a friend to try Miss Spider that her son really enjoyed it. My grand daughter watched it and i even caught myself watching it along with her..lol..I would highly recommend this dvd and its a great price for 3 dvds, you cant go wrong..As they grow older they will continue to watch it..
My three year old loves The Doodlebops! Great set, it keeps her occupied for hours! It has a variety of of shows so the parents don't get worn out on the movies either!

I don't know much about digital things, but it is very sandy.  Maybe it is copied from video tapes to dvd.
My boy is still watching, but if i knew this low quality, i would never buy this.
MY 5 YEAR OLD SON LOVES THE DOODLEBOPS. HE LOVES TO SING AND DANCE TO THEM. NEVER GETS TIRED OF THEM. I'VE BOUGHT THIS ITEM TWICE BECAUSE HE PLAYS IT SO MUCH IT GOT WORN OUT. GREAT BUY.
the dvd's arrived in perfect shape and in plenty of time for Christmas. I was very happy with the overall experience.
Everything was great gave to my great nephew his only one and not talking yet I hope he tells me later howmuch he likes the gift

This is the original Doodlebops (before being picked up by Disney) but the quality of entertainment for my daughter is the same.  Personally I enjoy picking out the differences in costumes, sets and even ears (had them in these episodes but were gone once disney took over), etc.  Helps me numb my mind to something I have seen and listened to over and over and over again.  :)  Overall, great entertainment for my 4 year old.
You CAN'T EVER go wrong with Miss Spiders Sunny Patch Friends for your child.  My son loves it.  It ALWAYS sends a good message, he learns from it, and it's VERY colorful!!  Fun at any early age...

Bob the builder dvd set is a great gift for my 18 month old..the only thing I don't like about it is that in one of the dvd's they change spud's voice and it does not nearly sound right! But the movies themselves are great and good lessons for children.

I will be the first to admit that I tried to steer my kids away from Barney :) But they persisted and when we finally got this set, they loved these DVDs...I even sat through them (I can't say so much for the Barney television shows). The video quality and sound are excellent. I would highly recommend them to anyone with toddlers/preschoolers.
I would be able to review it better if i wud have received my item! when my order was placed on oct 3rd and still not received.

Have received the product undamaged and in very good condition.
A speacial thanks to the seller for their great service.

This series is my daughter's favorite.  She is 2 years old, this is the one that keeps her attention the longest.  As a mother, I like the bright colors, the voices are calming, the action is perfect for little ones, and it makes my daughter laugh.
My grandkids enjoy these videos, however there is one of the 3 that is defective and stops playing. Will need to return this.

This is perfect for your doodlebop fan.  my daughter loves the doodlebops and wanted a dvd so she can watch them anytime since the disney channel no longer plays them. She couldn't decide which she wanted and we decided on this one since it came with treee and for such a great price.

Bob videos are so positive teaching children that they can do things, how to be polite and how to be just sweet people.
The videos are excellant.
Great little package, very happy with the pack, Great company to deal with.  I'm happy, happy, happy.
Martn calvo
I bought this for my 7 year old grandson.. He loves it - especially since the show changed the whole program
nice dvd set for a Bob the Builder fan
